Name: opentelemetry-instrumentation-asgi
Version: 0.18b0
Summary: ASGI instrumentation for OpenTelemetry
Home-page: https://github.com/open-telemetry/opentelemetry-python-contrib/instrumentation/opentelemetry-instrumentation-asgi
Author: OpenTelemetry Authors
Author-email: cncf-opentelemetry-contributors@lists.cncf.io
